category: Python
requires: python
sdesc: "Python distutils package manager"
ldesc: "Yolk is a Python tool for obtaining information about packages 
installed by distutils, setuptools and easy_install and packages on PyPI 
(Python Package Index a.k.a. The Cheese Shop).

Yolk can list all the packages installed by setuptools on your system,
show which packages are active, non-active or in development mode and
show you which have newer versions available according to PyPI."
